# TB-18 M0 retry evidence packaging policy:
# - Main chain (runtime_repo + cas) committed via runtime_repo.dotgit.tar.gz +
#   cas.dotgit.tar.gz tarballs (TB-7R/TB-8/TB-9 precedent per
#   feedback_evidence_packaging_policy_required).
# - Working tree files (non-.git) committed directly.
# - Tamper subdirs (one chain copy with flipped byte; intermediate audit
#   working trees) preserved as tarballs only (.dotgit.tar.gz); raw .git
#   dirs ignored to avoid git submodule semantics on re-checkout.
r1/P*/tamper/*/runtime_repo/.git/
r1/P*/tamper/*/cas/.git/
